<div class="main-and-aside r">
  
  <div class="main content-container" role="main">
    
      <div class="article-teaser">
        Over Christmas and New Year, most of the TfL network is open. However, today there are changes and planned works that may affect your journey.
        
      </div>
    
    <div class="on-this-page">
      <p>There are changes and planned works on the following services today. All our other services are running normally.</p>

<p>See our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-24T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-24T23%3a59%3a59">Status updates map for&nbsp;Monday 24&nbsp;December</a>&nbsp;for Tube, Overground, TfL Rail, DLR and tram services.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Tube</h2>

<p>There&nbsp;is a reduced service:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Weekday services are running. They&nbsp;are being&nbsp;reduced from about 15:00</li>
	<li>Most last trains&nbsp;are at Sunday times</li>
	<li>The Waterloo &amp; City line&nbsp;is running a&nbsp;reduced service all day, with last trains at about 23:15</li>
</ul>

<hr />
<h2>London Overground</h2>

<p>There are changes to services today:</p>

<ul>
	<li>On these routes,&nbsp;a weekday service will run, finishing from around 21:30:
	<ul>
		<li>between Highbury &amp; Islington and Crystal Palace / West Croydon</li>
		<li>between Dalston Junction and New Cross / Clapham Junction</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>On these routes, a weekday service will run until 12:00. Then a Saturday service will run, with services finishing from around 21:30
	<ul>
		<li>between Richmond / Clapham Junction and Stratford</li>
		<li>between Watford Junction and Euston</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li>No service between South Tottenham and Barking and a reduced service between Gospel Oak and South Tottenham. Trains will run about every 30 minutes</li>
	<li>No service between Romford and Upminster</li>
	<li>No service between&nbsp;Edmonton Green and Cheshunt</li>
	<li>Reduced service between&nbsp;Liverpool Street and Chingford (trains run about every 20 minutes, not stopping at Bethnal Green, Hackney Downs and Clapton)</li>
	<li>Reduced service between Liverpool Street and Edmonton Green/Enfield Town&nbsp;(trains run about&nbsp;every 20 minutes, not stopping at Bethnal Green, Cambridge Heath, London Fields and Hackney Downs)</li>
	<li>Please use replacement or local bus services - see our <a href="http://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-24T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-24T23%3a59%3a59#line-raillo-overground">status updates</a> page</li>
</ul>

<p>Follow <a href="http://twitter.com/LDNOverground">&#64;LDNOverground</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>TfL Rail</h2>

<p>There are no services running today.</p>

<p>Please use replacement or local buses. See our <a href="http://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-24T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-24T23%3a59%3a59#line-raillo-overground">status updates</a> page.</p>

<p>Follow <a href="http://twitter.com/TfLRail">&#64;TfLRail</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>DLR</h2>

<p>A Saturday service is running. Services will finish&nbsp;from around 22:00.</p>

<p>Follow <a href="https://twitter.com/LondonDLR"> &#64;LondonDLR</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Trams</h2>

<p>We are running a reduced service:</p>

<ul>
	<li>There is&nbsp;a Saturday service until 18:00.</li>
	<li>Trams run every 15 minutes on all routes between 18:00 and 20:00</li>
	<li>Trams run every 20 minutes between 20:00 and Saturday last trams</li>
</ul>

<p>Follow&nbsp;<a href="https://twitter.com/TramsLondon">&#64;TramsLondon</a> for news and service information</p>

<hr />
<h2>Buses</h2>

<p>We are running a Saturday service today.</p>

<ul>
	<li>There&nbsp;are no night services</li>
	<li>24-hour services finish around midnight; day buses&nbsp;are operating&nbsp;until normal last bus times</li>
	<li>There&nbsp;is an enhanced Saturday service on route 507</li>
	<li>On routes 521 and X68,&nbsp;there is a limited service</li>
</ul>

<p>See all today's planned bus changes on our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/bus/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-24T00%3A00%3A00&amp;endDate=2018-12-24T23%3A59%3A59">Bus status updates map for Monday 24 December</a>.</p>

<p>Follow <a href="https://twitter.com/TfLBusAlerts">&#64;TfLBusAlerts</a> for news and service information.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Driving</h2>

<ul>
	<li>The Congestion Charge and T-Charge apply today</li>
	<li>See our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/traffic/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-24T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-24T23%3a59%3a59">traffic status updates map for Monday 24 December</a></li>
</ul>

<p>Follow <a href="https://twitter.com/TfLTrafficNews">&#64;TfLTrafficNews</a> on Twitter.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Emirates Air Line</h2>

<p>Today the cable car is running 07:00-19:00.</p>

<p>Find out more in our <a href="/modes/emirates-air-line/index">Emirates Air Line</a> section, see <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/cable-car/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2018-12-24T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2018-12-24T23%3a59%3a59">Status updates for Emirates&nbsp;Air Line on 24 December</a>&nbsp;or <a href="https://twitter.com/EmiratesAirLDN">follow &#64;EmiratesAirLine on Twitter</a>.</p>

<hr />
<h2>Taxis &amp; minicabs</h2>

<p>For taxis (black cabs) there is an extra charge of &pound;4 if you're travelling between 20:00 tonight&nbsp;and 06:00 on Thursday 27 December. For private hire (including minicabs), there may be an extra charge - please check when you book.</p>

<hr />
<h2>River</h2>

<p>Thames Clipper services finish early, from&nbsp;19:30 at some piers&nbsp;tonight.</p>

<hr />
<h2>National Rail</h2>

<p>Check <a href="http://www.nationalrail.co.uk/christmas">National Rail's Christmas page</a> for information about all service changes and planned works over Christmas and New Year.</p>
      
           
      
      
        
          
